KAlarm

=== Version 0.2 --- 20 Oct 2001 ===
Implemented repeating alarms.
Added extra pair of arrow buttons to time spinbox to change the hour.
Fixed sorting by colour column.
Better What's This? texts for the main window.
Removed -r, -s short options (use --reset, --stop instead).
Updated libraries to kdepim-2.2.1.
Reinstated libkcal holidays files.

=== Version 0.1.1 --- 1 Sep 2001 ===
Fixed documentation not created by build.
Removed KOrganizer-specific files from libkcal (standalone package).
Changed alarm daemon icon (standalone package).

=== Version 0.1 --- 31 Aug 2001 ===
Initial release.
